reviews.text:
All of the food we‚Äôve ordered from Zorba‚Äôs has always been delicious!!  Recently we ordered chicken salad subs, which are always great but this time they were exceptional!! The chicken salad was served on a sesame seed roll.  It was fantastic!!
We have not eaten in the restaurant but have ordered and waited for our food. The staff was really friendly!  Generally we have our food delivered, which we get quickly. The delivery guy is great!!

Zorba‚Äôs why ? I ordered their ‚Äúspecial‚Äù that was XL Pizza , 2 Lg subs or wraps & 12 wings . I ordered an Italian COLD cut, you put it in the same bag as 2 orders of wings and a hot chicken cheesesteak. & why do you put the TOPPINGS on the bottom of the bread ? They‚Äôre called TOPPINGS. Bread is soggy and done. All you had to do was put what‚Äôs cold in a small separate bag and stop putting toppings on the bottom. I also didn‚Äôt get any sauce for the wings i ordered. The delivery man kept rushing me to sign his handled POS & I was trying to give him cash and bring the food inside and he kept rushing me. Weird.

Small, sauceless, burn wings and salty pizza...
I will say, the service when I walked in was great and the place looked, smelled, seemed really nice, got everything quickly. BUT, the wings are definitely not tossed in the sauce, it's like they put the wings in the box and they drizzle a spoonful of sauce on them. Also, unfortunately the wings were burnt/ blackened, very small compared to many other places I normally go and I had to pull a handful of little feathers from a few unlike other places. The pizza wasn't exactly bad but just tasted a little over salty for some reason? I used to love the place when they first opened years ago, even they had the like 30 some odd wing flavors but after they changed it was never the same. I decided to go back and try them out again since it had been forever ago I was last there and unfortunately tonight I was disappointed. I will certainly try the cheese steak and another pizza before deciding to completely avoid the place but don't see me every buying wings again sadly. Maybe it was an off night? but they just have never been the same as when they first opened.

Always enjoy my pizza and sub whenever I order with them! I usually pick it up, but got delivery this time and they were super quick, with my food hot and fresh!!!! And it was at 9pm on a Saturday! Thanks Zorba‚Äôs!!! It absolutely hit the spot!

Very good despite some reviews. We wanted to try different places in the area. We ordered for pick-up: chicken gyro, fish fillet sub, disco fries, broccoli bites, and a slice of rainbow cake (sorry not pictured, we already took a bite). Portions were nice! Variety of food on the menu. Nice portions. Lots to choose from. No complaints over here! We will be ordering again üòä

Ordered again 3/19 when my bestie came for a visit...she enjoyed her cheesesteak. The veggie calzone was very good. And ordered fried mushroom.

3/25 ordered the works. Yummy!

customerMoodAnalysis.sentimentSummary: Customer opinions are divided. The 3.4/5 rating from 5 recent reviews suggests some great experiences mixed with areas needing attention.

strengthsPerceived: Customers consistently praise the deliciousness and exceptional quality of Zorba's chicken salad subs, especially when served on a sesame seed roll. - social media marketing can showcase this strength
The quick and reliable delivery service, even during peak times like 9pm on a Saturday, ensures that food arrives hot and fresh. - Boostly marketing services can amplify this
Zorba's offers a wide variety of menu options with generous portions, satisfying diverse tastes and preferences. - SEO services can leverage this for better visibility
improvementOpportunities: Negative reviews regarding food quality and preparation (soggy bread, burnt wings, lack of sauce) - review management can address this concern
Inconsistent food quality and changes from past experiences - social media marketing can improve this area
Delivery service issues and customer interaction (rushed delivery experience) - Boostly marketing services can improve this
